# rz_y4_p — Rz(-p·π/8), Yoshida-4 half-ZZ coefficient rotation. analytic golden.
```python id=bloq
import numpy as np
from qualtran.bloqs.basic_gates import Rz
p=1/(4-4**(1/3)); q=1-4*p
bloq = Rz(-p*np.pi/8)
```
```python id=golden
import numpy as np
p=1/(4-4**(1/3)); q=1-4*p
golden = np.diag([np.exp(1j*p*np.pi/16), np.exp(-1j*p*np.pi/16)]).astype(complex)
```
